Class UniformRandomAnnotator<OBJECT,ANNOTATION>

  • java.lang.Object

  • Type Parameters:
    OBJECT - Type of object being annotated
    ANNOTATION - Type of annotation.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Classifier<ANNOTATION,OBJECT>, Annotator<OBJECT,ANNOTATION>, BatchTrainer<Annotated<OBJECT,ANNOTATION>>

    public class UniformRandomAnnotator<OBJECT,ANNOTATION>
extends BatchAnnotator<OBJECT,ANNOTATION>
    An annotator that chooses annotations completely randomly from the set of all known annotations. The number of annotations produced is set by the type of NumAnnotationsChooser used.
    Author:
    Jonathon Hare (jsh2@ecs.soton.ac.uk)
